data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning brick ranch is a true gem.  Step inside and be greeted by the elegance of hardwood floors that flow seamlessly through the home. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home offers some incredible living spaces from the  updated kitchen to The huge family room with a cozy  fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for those chilly evenings.there's plenty of space for the whole family to relax and unwind.    Enjoy the luxury of not one, but two full updated baths, ensuring your comfort and convenience. And let's not forget about the incredible backyard. Imagine endless possibilities for outdoor fun and relaxation in this private oasis with fresh landscaping  and incredible 6 foot fence for your privacy. More features  include a newly done roof 2 summers ago . Asphalt driveway and rain gutters done 3 months ago, laundry room on the main level and so much more. This property has EXCELLENT PROXIMITY TO HIGHLY-RATED SCHOOLS, SHOPPING, & RESTAURANTS, and it's just a SHORT DISTANCE TO THE EXPRESSWAY. This is a must see to appreciate and will not last long. Don't miss out and schedule your showing today!!!!!!
